info.name: Soul Land 2: Peerless Tang Sect
info.description: A strange continent in another world.  No magic, no battle qi, no martial arts, only martial spirits. Ten thousand years after the Tang clan was founded on the Douluo continent, the Tang clan has declined to the verge of extinction.  A whole new generation of proud talents has been born. Will the new generation of the Seven monsters of Shrek be able to reestablish the Tang Clan and compose a new tale of greatness for the unrivaled Tang Clan?

moreInfo.synonyms: The Unrivaled Tang Sect, Combat Continent II
